{"tid":1511218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關深水埗檢13枝懷疑不安全激光筆　禁店鋪出售","createTime":"2019-08-27T12:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T12:58:48.000Z","uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6dfea96cab6ceb5ad46aca1f8f093620240fdaa0","tid":1511218,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"海關得，消委會都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關在深水埗一間店舖檢獲13枝懷疑不安全激光筆，並發出禁制通知書，禁止繼續出售，調查仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n海關表示，有關店舖違反《消費品安全條例》及其附屬法例，於是在上星期五採取行動。海關表示，在今年3月進行試購行動，從一間零售店舖購買一款激光筆進行安全測試，並勒令該店將該款共13枝沒有標示雙語警告或警誡的激光筆儲存於指定的地方。測試結果顯示，該款激光筆沒有裝配相關安全控制裝置，同時亦只附有英文使用警告。<br />\n<br />\n海關提醒市民，由於該類激光筆所發出的光束，有機會損害眼睛和皮膚，在任何情況下都不應讓激光筆照射出的光點，射向眼睛。"},{"pid":"ec94fd028d66a8eeb6b815728be91bbd1e0c513d","tid":1511218,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxqHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=81383491\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxqHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=e838613d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxqHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=1f388cf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupr